creator: Samocat Sharing
descriptionHtml:
Samocat Sharing — automated kick-scooter sharing system.

The most compact city transport, working for you in 24/7 mode.
Kick scooters are easy, foldable, light and fun. We want everybody to enjoy it. Just when it is necessary. That's why we created the ultimate sharing system for kick scooters. Sharing station, kick scooters and smartphone app. Ready to ride.
